{"tid":346703,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 湯狀回帶：一地兩檢冇可能","createTime":"2017-08-04T07:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T08:23:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f093f9aa8e81e2f3cac11f4a578f9262fb53d69","tid":346703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170804/20111331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170804%2F20111331&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c07736d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170804%2F20111331&h=f41aea6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170804/20111331</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n湯狀回帶：一地兩檢冇可能<br />\n<br />\n4,807<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170804/large/a1306a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170804%2Flarge%2Fa1306a.gif&h=6195fb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■余若薇噚日喺facebook幫湯家驊重溫昨日的我。余若薇fb截圖<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n對於一地兩檢，資深大律師湯家驊指《基本法》第22條清楚寫明，中央政府各部門不得干預香港根據《基本法》自行管理嘅事情，亦不可在香港設立辦事處，以及要遵守香港的法律，又質疑政府究竟根據甚麼憲制條文或法律基礎，可以做到一地兩檢。<br />\n湯又話勉強要喺香港境內進行一地兩檢，將直接衝擊一國兩制，又引用《基本法》第14條話香港政府負責香港社會治安，第16條說明香港政府是負起區內行政管理權，第18條規定香港特區只可以實行香港法律，所以在香港市中心進行一地兩檢，「憲法上根本完全是沒可能！」<br />\n大家冇睇錯，上述嘅言論的確係出自湯家驊把口，不過係2009、2010年嘅湯家驊，唔係2017年入咗行政會議、支持一地兩檢嘅湯家驊。<br />\n<br />\n前黨友fb貼文<br />\n湯家驊舊戰友、公民黨余若薇都忍唔住喺fb幫湯回帶，話湯當日喺立會講明係市中心做一地兩檢，喺憲法上係完全冇可能。湯另一舊戰友、公民黨主席梁家傑亦同湯回帶，佢喺fb留低一句話：「當今大陸和香港最大的問題，就是讀過書應明理的知識份子，太多湯家驊，太少劉曉波！」  <br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 符傳富上任：chur過做Big Four (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 立會亂擺新咪兜捱鬧 (李八方)"},{"pid":"44963186251bcdae061d93641cdf332cf66eca16","tid":346703,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"湯狀回帶：一地兩檢冇可能<br />\n<br />\n十一隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc448347251945e9f43845fbb666fb364610177a","tid":346703,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>湯狀回帶：一地兩檢冇可能<br />\n<br />\n十一隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55faa6186c959e6585e17cb772b7a457a4c05cc","tid":346703,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"今天的我打倒昨日的我"},{"pid":"aedc8149ac4e9ef026e67288fb3d11321534f2c3","tid":346703,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"肯定比共匪渣住春袋啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750a203138b97dc858bd8f56af5cfa93e7cbe76d","tid":346703,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>湯狀回帶：一地兩檢冇可能<br />\n<br />\n十一隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n憲法上根本完全是沒可能!<br />\n十一哥緊係十一隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}